    <script>


        function togglePanel(object,showLabel,hideLabel) {

            var hiding = (object.dom.style.display != "none");

            var animationCallback = function() {
                if (hiding) {
                    document.getElementById(showLabel).style.display = "block";
                    document.getElementById(hideLabel).style.display = "none";
                } else {
                    document.getElementById(showLabel).style.display = "none";
                    document.getElementById(hideLabel).style.display = "block";
                }
             };

            var animationSettings = {useDisplay:true, duration:0.5, easing:"easeBoth", callback:animationCallback};

            if(hiding) {
                object.slideOut('t', animationSettings);
            } else {
                object.slideIn('t', animationSettings);
            }
        }         

        function attachDetachArticleToCaseBackToCaseStart(b) {
            if (b.isAttach) {
                attachArticleAndGoBackToCase();
            } else {
                detachArticleAndGoBackToCase();
            }
        }

        function goBackToCaseUrl() {
            if (false) {
                window.opener.location.reload(false);
                window.close();
            } else {
                window.location = '';
            }
        }

        function attachDetachArticleToCaseStart(b) {
            if (b.isAttach) {
                attachArticleToCase();
                b.isAttach = false;
                b.setText("Detach from case");
                if(true) {
                    b.backToCaseButton.isAttach = false;
                    b.backToCaseButton.setText("Detach and Return to case");
                }
            } else {
                detachArticleToCase();
                b.isAttach = true;
                b.setText("Attach to case");
                if(true) {
                    b.backToCaseButton.isAttach = true;
                    b.backToCaseButton.setText("Attach and Return to case");
                }
            }
        }
